In the first loop we will be checking p and the 1st word i the list. since they are different they go inside the loop and reduce the length to pl-1.
then the loop continue till the given both the words are the same. Aafter that it goes to the next(incremented word) for loop with the remaining in the p ad pl.
the it goes the same with the next word i the list and contiues till both are same, then it returs the required output.

